text: Zhitnoye () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Zhitninsky Selsoviet of Ikryaninsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 1,902 as of 2010.Всероссийская перепись населения 2010 года. 1.
